      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. It offers a smooth and reliable driving experience, with a clean interior and all major systems functioning as expected. While the exterior shows some minor signs of normal use, such as small stone chips and light surface scratches, the paint still retains a strong shine. This is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate work.",
