    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches, chips, or swirls, and the interior remains in pristine, original condition with no signs of wear. Every mechanical component has been meticulously maintained, and the car drives perfectly with a full, documented service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and treated with the utmost care.",
